Wicked Jazz Sounds is both a community of DJs, musicians, dancers, VJs and a party organiser. It has performed in the major Dutch clubs like Paradiso, Melkweg, 013, Panama, Hotel Arena, Nighttown and many more venues and festivals. It also features the Wicked Jazz Sounds club night in the Sugar Factory, Amsterdam every Sunday.

Wicked Jazz Sounds is organised by DJ Phil Horneman and Manne van der Zee since the winter of 2001. DJ Phil Horneman has been using the name Wicked Jazz Sounds since 1998 for a radio show on local radio. Together they decided to use their years of personal experience and expertise in nightlife and music to do exactly what they really wanted to do: They started their own Wicked Jazz Sounds-organisation.
